{"tid":671374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"揚言想殺台灣同學　中國女留學生被送精神病院","createTime":"2018-05-20T05:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T00:34:10.000Z","uid":41404,"like":89,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"01156d2ffd4166c824cb3e024b525b89bfa4ea31","tid":671374,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T05:47:16.000Z","msg":"中國女留學生「C.N. Hsu」，因為不滿學校多名台灣同學，不認為自己是中國人，本月9日在《臉書》上發出死亡威脅，揚言：「真想殺死這些台獨份子」。被威脅的台灣女學生得知後，向警方報案，結果Hsu不但被學校勒令退學，還被澳洲警方送進精神病院。<br />\n <br />\nHsu的臉書顯示，她因為向「支持台獨」的女同學生發出死亡威脅，結果被勒令退學，還被警方「關瘋人院」好幾天，而她「出院」後，今天（19日）要被遣送回中國。她指，家人勸她不要待在澳洲，但她不想回共匪淪陷區（中國），不希望過著沒有臉書、Google、YouTube、Instagram、推特、tumblr及Yahoo的生活，也不願吸暗無天日的空氣，最好能到雪梨台灣外省人的公司工作。一想到今天就要被遣返，徹夜未眠。<br />\n <br />\nHsu雖然來自中國南京，但自稱「澳洲中國國民黨議員」。從她的臉書可見，她雖然反對台獨，但也不認同共匪，認為中華民國才代表中國，才是她的祖國。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180520/1357341/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180520%2F1357341%2F&d=m2sT9J4EWVKnSDdTd08woAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=a96c6c2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180520%2F1357341%2F&h=6a0c5fb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180520/1357341/</a>"},{"pid":"7c8f2377bfb7486c55f9ebe740c1a0c98cc8e8e4","tid":671374,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T05:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f52ceac33490be2a7f69213c521c4c85f1cb54","tid":671374,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T05:51:28.000Z","msg":"台灣人當然是正宗中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019cf34a7b67c61f63b1d7762ab6ee66acf61bcd","tid":671374,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"